					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Some other slight optimizations:
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">ASL reg/mem ; clear bit 0<br />LSR reg/mem ; clear bit 7<br />INC/DEC mem&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;; toggle bit 0<br />ASL reg&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;; put bit 7 into carry, and bit 6 into N flag<br />CMP #$80&nbsp; &nbsp; ; put bit 7 into carry, without modifying A<br />CMP #1&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ; set carry if A is not zero</div></div>

					
							<br /><br />
